channel.title: New song and style - You Me At Six
channel.description:
Hey Guys,
As you probably know these guys are my favourite band and today at 8pm they released a new song titled "Sweet Feet". Now i absoloutly love this song and its different from their usual stuff.
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dvrpA904Pbc
If you like i think they would like you to send them feedback at http://www.myspace.com/youmeatsix
thanks
- Harvey
P.s. Guess who gets to see that song on its 1st proper live performance :p
